        {
            "title": "阿根廷債券上演過山車 美國重申支持但強調不會直接投錢",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"562\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/jf4gb1dppJD5fRwyx0k7KQ--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTU2MjtjZj13ZWJw/https://media.zenfs.com/en/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/c27f18af8148f66bfb0a50bd077de6a0\" width=\"960\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><br/></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span class=\"news-dateline\">【彭博】--</span> 美國財政部長斯科特·貝森特周四重申對<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link\" data-ylk=\"slk:阿根廷;sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link;itc:0\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/tag/阿根廷\">阿根廷</a>的支持，但隨後警告稱任何援助都不包括美國直接投資，引發阿根廷債券價格大幅波動。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">外匯市場相對更為穩定，主要因為哈維爾·米萊政府連續第三天拋售美元以捍衛披索。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">貝森特周四早些時候在X上表示，美國將「採取必要措施」幫助阿根廷，帶動其債券大漲。隨後不久，他對CNBC表示，這並不意味著要向該國投入資金，這一補充又令債券回落。再之後，有報導稱米萊政府的高層官員將赴華盛頓磋商，債券再度走高。</p><div class=\"bg-card-bg-1 -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-7226e5be-4862-33a5-8e18-837e64ec92e3-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">美國此前已提出至少三種援助這個危機頻頻的南美國家的可能方案，包括提供200億美元的互換額度、回購阿根廷債務以及直接購買貨幣。貝森特的最新表態似乎縮小了範圍。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">他在接受CNBC採訪時表示：「我們將給他們提供互換額度，但不會把錢投到阿根廷。」</p><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\" \" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"562\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/C1aX4MtxrkUuLezChaB6cg--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTU2MjtjZj13ZWJw/https://media.zenfs.com/en/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/595a5d1d7c96070f74db024ec1ceda2f\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\"> </figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">阿根廷本地媒體報導稱，該國經濟部長Luis Caputo和央行行長Santiago Bausili將於周五抵達美國討論貨幣互換協議。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">推薦閱讀：阿根廷資產再遭拋售 美國財長貝森特的市場安撫者角色面臨考驗</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題Bessent Touts Swap, Not ‘Money,’ as Argentina Shores Up Peso</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">--聯合報導 Jorgelina Do Rosario.</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2025 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E9%98%BF%E6%A0%B9%E5%BB%B7%E5%82%B5%E5%88%B8%E4%B8%8A%E6%BC%94%E9%81%8E%E5%B1%B1%E8%BB%8A-%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B%E9%87%8D%E7%94%B3%E6%94%AF%E6%8C%81%E4%BD%86%E5%BC%B7%E8%AA%BF%E4%B8%8D%E6%9C%83%E7%9B%B4%E6%8E%A5%E6%8A%95%E9%8C%A2-202609402.html",
